卢比奥最初得到了[[茶党运动|茶党]]的强烈支持而當選美国参议院议员，但因为他在2013年參與的兩黨參議員組成的「{{link-en|八人會|Gang of Eight (immigration)}}」（Gang of Eight）所提出的移民改革法案，导致茶党对他的支持有所降低<ref>[http://news.yahoo.com/factbox-republican-2016-presidential-field-swells-14-christie-180536168.html Factbox: Republican 2016 presidential field swells to 14 with Christie] {{Wayback|url=http://news.yahoo.com/factbox-republican-2016-presidential-field-swells-14-christie-180536168.html |date=20151220161358 }}, [[Reuters|Reuters]] (June 30, 2015): "He was swept into the Senate in the Tea Party wave of 2010 but has fought to strengthen ties with conservatives after he helped lead a failed push for comprehensive immigration reform in 2013."</ref><ref name="MakTeaParty">Tim Mak, [http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2015/04/13/tea-partiers-rage-against-rubio-2016.html Tea Partiers Rage Against Rubio 2016] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2015/04/13/tea-partiers-rage-against-rubio-2016.html |date=20151117085228 }}, ''Daily Beast'' (April 13, 2015).</ref>。《{{link-en|国家杂志|National Journal}}》（National Journal）在2013年将他列为排名第17位保守的参议员<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.mcclatchydc.com/news/politics-government/election/article24780745.html | publisher=McClatchyDC | title=Sen. Marco Rubio sees opportunity for redemption on the right | date=2015-02-26 | access-date=2015-11-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017193925/http://www.mcclatchydc.com/news/politics-government/election/article24780745.html | archive-date=2015-10-17 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

卢比奥反对枪械管制、同性婚姻和堕胎（强奸和乱伦的情况例外），亦反对[[第13769号行政命令|川普禁止部分国家国民入境]]。他主张增加国防预算，重启[[关塔那摩监狱|关塔那摩监狱]]并将抓捕的恐怖份子关押在里面。<ref>{{Cite news| url = https://www.bostonglobe.com/opinion/2016/02/04/don-call-marco-rubio-moderate/24kSg4Ow5CDMoQ93a1a67I/story.html| title = Don’t call Marco Rubio ‘moderate’| publisher = The Boston Globe| date = 2016-02-04| accessdate = 2016-02-05| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160205092631/http://www.bostonglobe.com/opinion/2016/02/04/don-call-marco-rubio-moderate/24kSg4Ow5CDMoQ93a1a67I/story.html| archive-date = 2016-02-05| dead-url = no}}</ref>

2019年年底，參議員卢比奥提議，要求禁止聯邦基金投資中企。

卢比奥為美國參議院中的對[[中國共產黨|中國共產黨]]強硬派的代表人物，在其任期內大力推行《[[維吾爾人權政策法案|維吾爾人權政策法案]]》及《[[香港人權民主法案|香港人權民主法案]]》。

==外交政策==
